                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2 relative before:content-['•'] before:text-black dark:before:text-white before:mr-2 before:absolute before:left-0">
                            Access the latest news and updates from our HBA community.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2 relative before:content-['•'] before:text-black dark:before:text-white before:mr-2 before:absolute before:left-0">
                            Discover upcoming retreats and events tailored for you.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 py-2 relative before:content-['•'] before:text-black dark:before:text-white before:mr-2 before:absolute before:left-0">
